{"id": 2235, "genre": 1000, "title": "哪些二手交易的糟糕体验最让你不满?", "description": "在不，包邮不，能便宜点不。", "record_count": 6242, "comment_count": 24, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2018031916314329IZDoYb56UOJB0h.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-03-19T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3885, "title": "哪些二手交易的糟糕体验最让你不满?", "content": "二手交易的哪些不好体验曾让你不满？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 271302, "content": "客服难当，说了不包邮不议价，买家还是上来就砍价", "image": "img/option/option/20180319163840rhzkOKGwoHgZLcbe.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 271304, "content": "新旧程度成迷，“8成新”模糊程度堪比外卖界的“微辣”", "image": "img/option/option/20180319164028czVNvxPG3dUZBaiK.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 271305, "content": "售后困难，没有有效的解决途径，总觉得二手就算了 ", "image": "img/option/option/20180319164255sMONH2pi9jehb4QF.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 271309, "content": "真假难辨，看了很多辨识贴也拿不准", "image": "img/option/option/20180319164732F2B8a7iegcVL4k0z.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 271311, "content": "图片参考价值打折，只有广告图或修图过度的照片", "image": "img/option/option/20180319165000orU73BxfadcIhqAP.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 271312, "content": "关键词，卖家标题五花八门，不少东西搜索不到", "image": "img/option/option/20180319165151DUjGJgFwxtu0kYeT.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 271313, "content": "沟通跨度长，一次留言七八个小时后才回复", "image": "img/option/option/201803191656395GzofJ79pP1BdrlC.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 271314, "content": "尺码难题，很多国外商品尺寸跟国内标准转换不清", "image": "img/option/option/201803191658142TqbFiERGoaJUSpH.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}